{"abstract":[{"text":"If you want to bring your creativity, passion, and technical expertise to the iBookstore, it may seem like there’s a vast array of web technologies to master. Gain a solid understanding of the HTML, CSS, and DOM technologies that are most relevant to book development, whether you’re creating a book with EPUB or building a custom widget for iBooks Author. See how to create beautiful text that is always laid out perfectly, gain a deep understanding of CSS positioning to create exceptional fixed-layout books, find out how to enrich your content with CSS animations, and learn which DOM operations are critical to adding enhancements with ease.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"title":"HTML, CSS, and DOM for Book Authors","role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC12","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"kind":"article","sections":[],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2012\/515\/"}},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc12-515-html-css-and-dom-for-book-authors"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12-515-HTML-CSS-and-DOM-for-Book-Authors"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","d